{"tid":1536522,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[一齊發毒誓] 話絕對唔會原諒警察嘅全部入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:56:10.000Z","uid":75514,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a593d1058ea944b3477215d1d262612ca02390","tid":1536522,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:18:13.000Z","msg":"同我一齊發呢個毒誓，讀咗呢段誓詞佢：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「謹此起誓，絕不原諒任何一個喺2019年6月12日或之後仍然係或加入香港警隊嘅人，生生世世概為不共戴天嘅仇敵，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>每年生日願望都必須要包括祝佢哋全家上下，對上一代，對落三代，全部不得好死</ins></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n如有違此誓，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">生腎石生足三十年</span>，<span style=\"color: green;\">終身排洩系統失效</span>，<span style=\"color: brown;\">手腳殘廢</span>，<span style=\"color: violet;\">脊椎變形</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">骨刺長壓神經</span>，<span style=\"color: teal;\">全身皮膚潰爛流膿</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">長命百歲</span></strong>。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我係認真嘅，出呢個post之前已經發咗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86107983ccf8bc2f524d9b5f9d8d2fcda16bd76","tid":1536522,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\